## 📝 Overview
This repository hosts the **Emotion-Based Music Recommendation System**, an intelligent application that detects a user's facial emotions and recommends music tailored to their current mood. By analyzing facial features from an image, the system creates a personalized and emotionally resonant music listening experience.

